### Variables
@baseUrl = https://qjfygjtondljywhbqbfj.supabase.co/functions/v1

### Test 1 - RSVP via token (cas nominal - public)
POST {{baseUrl}}/guests-rsvp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "invitation-token-here",
  "rsvp_status": "accepted"
}

### Test 2 - RSVP via guest_id (authentifié)
POST {{baseUrl}}/guests-rsvp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "guest_id": "guest-uuid-here",
  "rsvp_status": "declined"
}

### Test 3 - RSVP via GET (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/guests-rsvp?token=invitation-token-here&rsvp_status=maybe

### Test 4 - Erreur: paramètres manquants
POST {{baseUrl}}/guests-rsvp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rsvp_status": "accepted"
}

### Test 5 - Erreur: statut invalide
POST {{baseUrl}}/guests-rsvp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "invitation-token-here",
  "rsvp_status": "invalid_status"
}

### Test 6 - Erreur: token invalide
POST {{baseUrl}}/guests-rsvp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "invalid-token",
  "rsvp_status": "accepted"
}

